ygData.messageBody:
LOL! That's always my thought as well. Like many others I go for the
no-headgear option unless I'm in the thick of it. If you see me running
across Norrath with my helm on please remind me to take the scrapyard hood
ornament reject thing off, thanks!

Kitasi
